replies.body:
Gosh, just dodge them. Don't you know the skills are balanced if you look at the rate at which they're landed **and** how much damage they do? You can't just look at their damage.

If they only land 50% of the time, then when they're doing 500 damage, it's actually as if they're only do 250 damage! So his full combo is actually only hitting you for 30% of your max life. So it's balanced!
{{sticker:sg-miss-fortune}}
